<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Network Infrastructure | Aviation Eagle</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="https://media.aviationeagle.co.uk/favicon.ico">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .premium-panel {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
        }
        .premium-panel:hover {
            border-color: #f97316; /* Orange 500 */
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px -10px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.08);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="text-neutral-800 min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-between antialiased selection:bg-orange-500/10 selection:text-orange-600">

    <header class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6">
        <div class="py-2 flex items-center justify-center">
            <img src="https://media.aviationeagle.co.uk/Aviation-Eagle-Compact-TM-RBG.png" alt="Aviation Eagle Logo" class="h-12 md:h-14 w-auto object-contain">
        </div>
        <div>
            <a href="https://aviationeagle.co.uk" class="text-[11px] text-neutral-400 hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors duration-300 tracking-widest uppercase font-semibold">Main Hub &rarr;</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 flex-grow flex flex-col justify-center w-full">
        
        <div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full w-fit mb-8 mx-auto md:mx-0">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-emerald-700">Infrastructure Operational</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-light tracking-tight text-neutral-900 mb-6 text-center md:text-left leading-tight">
            Gestione Network & Routing Mail <br>
            <span class="font-normal text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-neutral-900 via-neutral-800 to-orange-600">aviationeagle.net</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-base text-neutral-500 font-light mb-12 max-w-2xl text-center md:text-left leading-relaxed">
            Il trasferimento e l'ottimizzazione strutturale dei nostri sistemi digitali sono completati. L'estensione <code class="text-neutral-900 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-neutral-50 text-sm border border-neutral-200 font-medium">.net</code> è ora pienamente operativa come dorsale (backbone) isolata per la gestione delle comunicazioni esterne e dei record MX del network.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            
            <div class="premium-panel p-8 rounded-xl">
                <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-orange-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 border border-orange-100">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 01-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0112 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 01-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 013 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 011.043-3.296 3.746 3.746 0 013.296-1.043A3.746 3.746 0 0112 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 013.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 011.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0121 12z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Infrastruttura Mail Attiva</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 font-light leading-relaxed">
                    Il dominio ospita interamente i server di posta elettronica del gruppo. La migrazione garantisce massima stabilità, isolamento del traffico e l'applicazione rigida dei protocolli di sicurezza avanzati (<span class="font-medium text-neutral-700">SPF, DKIM, DMARC</span>) già propagati con successo.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="premium-panel p-8 rounded-xl">
                <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-neutral-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 border border-neutral-200">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-neutral-800" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 17.25v1.007a3 3 0 01-.879 2.122L7.5 21h9l-.621-.621A3 3 0 0115 18.257V17.25m6-12V15a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 013 15V5.25m18 0A2.25 2.25 0 0018.75 3H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 003 5.25m18 0V12a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 013 12V5.25" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Isolamento dei Servizi</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 font-light leading-relaxed">
                    Mantenendo l'hub editoriale principale separato dai record di rete puri, assicuriamo che i carichi di lavoro legati alle comunicazioni non influenzino l'accessibilità o le performance di caricamento della piattaforma su <code class="text-neutral-700 font-medium">.co.uk</code>.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 border-l-2 border-emerald-500 pl-4 py-1 text-xs text-neutral-400 font-light tracking-wide italic">
            Configurazione completata. Record MX allineati su tutti i nodi globali.
        </div>

    </main>

    <footer class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-8 border-t border-neutral-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-[11px] text-neutral-400 tracking-wider">
        <p>
            &copy; 2026 Aviation Eagle Network. Gruppo editoriale non-profit.
        </p>
        <div class="flex space-x-6 font-medium text-neutral-500">
            <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span> DNS: Active</span>
            <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span> MX-Routing: Active</span>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
